 complement citations as indicators of impact. Social theories, on the other\nhand, are discussed because there is an inherent social aspect to the\nmeasurements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Feb 2015 20:54:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-20"}
