e and macro-causality and that the latter\nensures that the superluminalities found in the low energy effective theory are\nabsent in the full theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Feb 2015 20:59:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-20"}
