e related guaranteed minimum withdrawal\nbenefit contract is not convexity preserving, and hence does not satisfy the\nbang-bang principle other than in certain degenerate cases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Feb 2015 23:02:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 28 Feb 2015 20:34:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 14 Oct 2015 12:11:08 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 4 Nov 2015 21:39:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-06"}
