earing once. We also study an intrinsic symmetry action on the\nsingularities, in analogy with Slodowy's work for the regular nilpotent orbit.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Feb 2015 04:48:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Jul 2015 15:01:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 8 Sep 2016 14:32:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-09"}
