nt azimuthal field observed for both targets it is concluded that a\ndistributed dynamo operates in these moderately rotating Sun-like stars, in\nmarked contrast to the Sun's interface-layer dynamo.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Feb 2015 07:10:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
