f ZnSb might also control the thermoelectric properties of\nelectron poor semiconductors, such as Zn4Sb3, CdSb, Cd4Sb3, Cd13-xInyZn10, and\nZn5Sb4In2-x.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Feb 2015 15:25:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-23"}
